com.ibm.team.scm.common.dto
Interface IReadScope

All Known Subinterfaces:
IContributorDeferringScope, IPrivateScope, IProcessAreaScope, IPublicScope, ITeamAreaPrivateScope, IUnknownScope
public interface IReadScope

Describes an arbitrary visibility. When callers query objects of this type, they should start by asking #getReadPermissionMode() to determine the subclass to cast to.

Describes visibility of SCM items. In a nutshell:

Owned ByScopeRepresented by
contribprivatePrivateScope
contribpublicPublicScope
contribprocess areaContributorDeferringScope
project areaprocess area privateProcessAreaScope
team areaprocess area privateProcessAreaScope
team areateam area privateTeamAreaPrivateScope
anythingprivateIUnknownScope

Since:
0.8.1.
